<div class="card">
  <h4>ABOUT</h4>
  <p>Bianchi's Brews has beers made by Greek houses from across the U.S. Click on your favorite ambrosia to see details. If you're a college student who's recently imbibed one of these fantastic fermented libations and gotten stumbling, black-out drunk because you're young and don't yet know your limits, leave a review and tell us what you thought. Did you wake up next to a goat in South Dakota again? Did you accidently sell another of your kidneys? Bianchi's Brews wants to know.</p>
</div>

<h1>most reviewed</h1>
NAME: <%= @most_reviewed.name %>
# of REVIEWS: <%= @most_reviewed.reviews.length %>



<div class="card">
  <div class="card-header">
    <small><%= link_to "ADD BREW", new_brew_path %></small>
  </div>
  <div class="column">
    <h1>ALL BEERS</h1>
    <% @brews.each do |brew| %>
      <small><%= link_to brew.name, brew_path(brew) %></small><br>
    <% end %>
  </div>
  <div class="column">
    <h1>RECENTLY ADDED BEERS</h1>
    <% @seven_most_recent.each do |brew| %>
      <small><%= link_to brew.name, brew_path(brew) %></small><br>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
